Homepage: https://github.com/tomnomnom/waybackurls
Description: Fetch known URLs from Wayback Machine archives
 Extract historical URLs from Wayback Machine with:
 - Domain-based URL discovery
 - Subdomain enumeration
 - Timestamp filtering
 - JSON output support
